_sText:
Elivator prefabs

includes the elivater , shaft sections , and exits

its not funtional since you have to stack the number of sections your need !

to start , place the exit on the base , add the elivator inside that and stack as many sections you need adding in exits at floors you need

1 section = 1 floor

may need to scale it to the building you have if yours if taller or shorter than the prefabs


*can be used in CSS,DODS,HL2,HL2DM mapping

based off a HL2 elivator
